  <brief_title>Gynecomastia Extension Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>An OptioExtension of Trial 1033US/0006 to Assess Safety, Tolerability, Efficacy of Anastrozole (ZD1033, Arimidex™) in Treatment of Gynecomastia in Pubertal Boys Given Placebo and to Conduct a Long-Term Safety Follow-Up of Non-Responding Subjects Given Anastrozole in the Previous Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
