  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to look at the effect of anastrozole (ZD1033, Arimidex™) in
      reducing gynecomastia in pubertal boys treated with placebo in Trial 1033US/0006 (another
      anastrozole study).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
